                        <ul>
                            <li>Shanghai is continuously improving its business environment, and will implement the three major tasks in 2019 (i.e. expansion of the free trade zone, the launch of a technology innovation board and the integration of the Yangtze River Delta.)</li>
                            <li>The world economy is slowing down due to the rise of trade protectionism.</li>
                            <li>The tax reform that cuts tax and administrative fees has brought down the financial revenue the city takes in.</li>
                            <li>Shanghai's undergoing a phase of economic restructuring and upgrading by slowing down industrial growth. It demands more efforts to make breakthroughs in key technologies and create new drivers of economic growth.</li>
